@node Oprogramu "About"
AutoRun is a small commodity and what does it do?

AutoRun check immediately internal diskdrive and if you insert some
DOS diskette, its look For the @{B}script-file@{UB} @{"s/Auto-StartUp" link autostartup}. If the
script exists then will be executed.
@endnode


