@node history "History"


@{B}version 1.0@{UB}      - Initial release (not public)
    Very simple @{"AutoRun" link Oprogramu}, no commodity, no tooltypes, no quit..

    @{I}Size : @{UI}2600 b


@{B}version 2.00@{UB}     - the next release
    Some tooltypes added
    Now is commodity
    Quit with HotKey

    @{I}Size : @{UI}12616 b


@{B}version 3.00@{UB}
    in version 2.00 was a bug - fixed
    ToolType @{B}CX_POPKEY@{UB} removed, now quit If you run @{"AutoRun" link Oprogramu} again

    @{I}Size : @{UI}10120 b


@{B}version 3.05@{UB}
